name: Designing Miami
overview: Eilyn and Ray Jimenez, two designers from Miami are competitors, and a married couple.

episodes.name: Welcome to Miami
episodes.overview: Eilyn and her team give a former NFL player's house an upgrade. Ray wraps up work on a luxurious French Colonial home on the waterfront.

episodes.name: Delivering The Sexy
episodes.overview: Eilyn scrambles to finish EJ's home before he returns from vacation. Ray struggles to share his team with a former business partner.

episodes.name: The Job Offer
episodes.overview: After offering Steven a full-time position, Ray anxiously awaits a response. Eilyn guides Camila through a last-minute project in Fort Lauderdale.

episodes.name: Clash of the Designers
episodes.overview: Eilyn faces new roadblocks as she renovates a home for a couple — and one for their pet snake. Juggling several projects, Ray finds himself understaffed.

episodes.name: Cracks in the Foundation
episodes.overview: Eilyn prepares a luxury beachfront condo for a photo shoot. Ray continues the search for new employees and his own office space.

episodes.name: Biggest Project Yet
episodes.overview: As progress falters on the Jimenezes' own home, the Sire team botches an important proposal. Ray channels his newfound energy into a longtime project.

episodes.name: Ready to Launch
episodes.overview: Eilyn rewards her team’s hard work as Sire takes on a lavish Miami Beach project. A remodel with a quick turnaround time proves challenging for Ray.
